# {{.Name}}

A workflow engine UI plugin that serves a React frontend under `/plugins/{{.Name}}/`.

## Build

### 1. Build the UI

```bash
cd ui
npm install
npm run build
```

This produces `ui/dist/`, which is embedded into the plugin binary.

### 2. Build the plugin binary

```bash
go build -o {{.Name}}.plugin .
```

## Usage

Reference this plugin from your workflow config:

```yaml
requires:
  plugins:
    - name: {{.Name}}
      path: ./{{.Name}}.plugin
```

The plugin UI will be available at `http://your-server/plugins/{{.Name}}/`.

## Development

Edit files in `ui/src/` and run `npm run dev` for hot-reload during development.

